          "markText": "他如此恐惧，穿着湿透的破烂衣服，浑身是抓伤和淤青，脸色苍白，因兴奋而瞪大了眼睛，凝视着队长，仿佛在期盼他的救赎。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1767931632,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-01-09 12:07:12",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7970&rangeEnd=8026",
