    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "第二章",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300190369_4_5538-5662",
          "range": "5538-5662",
          "rangeStart": 5538,
          "rangeEnd": 5662,
          "markText": "就在这样的某个瞬间，他突然萌生了一个念头：若要摆脱这份不适感，便要铲除遥远德里纳河上那个苦难与不幸不断堆积的渡口——他要在那里架起一座桥梁，连接陡峭的河岸与凶险的河水，贯通被截断的道路，将波斯尼亚与东方、自己的故土与人生的舞台永远且稳固地连接起来。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1767931627,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-01-09 12:07:07",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5538&rangeEnd=5662",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5538&rangeEnd=5662"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_24_10761-10804",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "10761-10804",
      "markText": "紧接着，又有三枚手榴弹爆炸：两枚落入水中，一枚再次击中大桥，落在拥挤的人群与马匹之间。",
      "totalCount": 1192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10761&rangeEnd=10804",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10761&rangeEnd=10804"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_8_6697-6727",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6697-6727",
      "markText": "在这场斗争中，敌对双方不仅抢夺女人、马匹和武器，还抢夺民歌。",
      "totalCount": 1190,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6697&rangeEnd=6727",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6697&rangeEnd=6727"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_20_2620-2658",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2620-2658",
      "markText": "只在一部分人心中留下了隐秘的失望，在另一部分人心中埋下了对未来的疑虑与恐惧。",
      "totalCount": 1188,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2620&rangeEnd=2658",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2620&rangeEnd=2658"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_6_7334-7360",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7334-7360",
      "markText": "但此刻，当他无法动弹时，他开始幻想自己被钉在木桩上；",
      "totalCount": 1186,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7334&rangeEnd=7360",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7334&rangeEnd=7360"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_23_4250-4309",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "4250-4309",
      "markText": "而商店的大部分商品，则存放在铺面后方的房间里，需通过一扇低矮的铁门进入。",
      "totalCount": 1180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4250&rangeEnd=4309",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4250&rangeEnd=4309"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_7_2524-2607",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2524-2607",
      "markText": "旅人只能自行打理驿站，仅为了自身和牲畜的基本需求进行清扫，但每个人离开时，都会留下比来时更多的垃圾和混乱，等待下一个人清理——就像他们自己也曾清理前人留下的狼藉一样。",
      "totalCount": 1178,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2524&rangeEnd=2607",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2524&rangeEnd=2607"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_3_3080-3135",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3080-3135",
      "markText": "具体而言，桥中央的桥柱顶部向外延伸，两侧各悬挑出一座平台，大胆而规整地脱离桥身的直线，伸向湍急碧绿的河水上方。",
      "totalCount": 1176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3080&rangeEnd=3135",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3080&rangeEnd=3135"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_15_3675-3741",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "3675-3741",
      "markText": "起义领袖试图与外国建立联系，尤其是与土耳其帝国，声称占领当局超越了柏林会议赋予的权限，无权在仍处于土耳其宗主权之下的被占领土上征兵。",
      "totalCount": 1172,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3675&rangeEnd=3741",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3675&rangeEnd=3741"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_19_3032-3133",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "3032-3133",
      "markText": "这座位于塞尔维亚边境、距离土耳其边境不远，且通过深厚纽带与这两个国家中的一方或双方相连的小镇，感受到了这些变动，经历了这些变动，也解读着这些变动——尽管人们没有公开谈论，也没有直白地说出自己的所思所感。",
      "totalCount": 1172,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=3032&rangeEnd=3133",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=3032&rangeEnd=3133"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_8_2245-2271",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2245-2271",
      "markText": "起义者绕过乌日策，抵达了距离小镇仅两小时路程的地方。",
      "totalCount": 1170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300190369&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2245&rangeEnd=2271",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/294327d0813abb0dcg019d11?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2245&rangeEnd=2271"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300190369_8_2271-2310",
